<p><span class="anchor" id="p50"></span>غَيرهَا عِنْد مِنْبَر الْجَامِع<a href="#p50" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p51"></span>وتلاعن<a href="#p51" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p52"></span>حائص بِبَاب الْمَسْجِد وذمى فى بيعَة وكنيسة وَكَذَا بَيت نَار مَجُوسِيّ فى الاصح<a href="#p52" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p53"></span>وَمُقَابِله لَا يُلَاعن فِيهِ اذ لَيْسَ لَهُ حُرْمَة<a href="#p53" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p54"></span>لَا بَيت أصنام وثنى<a href="#p54" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
